      '<ul><li><strong>Realized</strong> profit comes from positions you&rsquo;ve sold.</li><li><strong>Unrealized</strong> profit is the paper gain or loss on positions you still hold.</li><li>The breakdown groups results by asset type where applicable.</li></ul>',
      '<h3>Step-by-step</h3>',
      '<ol><li>Open the dashboard and locate the Total Profits card.</li><li>Note the split between realized and unrealized.</li><li>Change the timeframe to see profits over 1D, 1M, 6M, or 1Y.</li><li>Compare against the performance chart to sanity-check the numbers.</li></ol>',
